<p><a href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/cheatsheet-notes-widget/id914665829">Cheatsheet</a> is available for Apple devices including watch app. Itâ€™s a single purpose app that you can keep secret and personal information that you just donâ€™t want to keep in Notes and canâ€™t find when you need it. I uses it quite often on my Apple watch with a quick glance and uses it as keyboard for some info like Address I have to type it quite often.</p>

