<p>Alexa is the best smart virtual assistant available and IMO, it is  a better option than Apple HomePod or Google Home  in terms of 3rd party integration availability and functionalities. You donâ€™t need expensive Alexa speaker. If you have bluetooth speaker, basic Echo Dot can become a powerful speaker by just saying â€œ<em>Alexa Bluetooth</em>â€</p>

